## 2. Implementation Standards
- Produce complete, production-ready code. No placeholders.
- After writing code, immediately write or update the corresponding tests.
- Reference the @pairx_prd_creation_c0d00ac2.plan.md and @pairx_implementation_tasks_58bd4467.plan.md for every decision to ensure alignment with the vision.

